title: Buffalo Bills, Arizona Cardinals are the teams you don't want to play in the playoffs (Brady Quinn Football Show 12/29)
description:
With the playoffs coming soon, who are the teams that top seeds like Green Bay and Kansas City want to avoid in a one-game playoff format. Will Brinson and Brady Quinn believe that to be Arizona and Buffalo, find out why in a brand new episode of the Brady Quinn football show. 

(05:57) Carson Wentz out due to COVID-19, what now?
(14:29) What teams in the AFC do you not want to play?
(28:40) What team in the NFC would you want to avoid in the playoffs?
(32:33) The Jacksonville Jaguars need to fully clean house
